The paper deals with the problem of answering Boolean conjunctive queries on uncertain databases, which is a topic in the field of databases (cs.DB). The paper also uses concepts from logic (cs.LO) and complexity theory (cs.CC) to analyze the tractability of the problem. Additionally, the paper discusses the relationship between this problem and probabilistic databases, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS).
